        "The output shows that for each call to `complex_operation`, the decorator first prints the execution time (corresponding roughly to the `duration` argument due to `time.sleep`) before the result of the multiplication is printed. This clearly illustrates how the decorator added the timing functionality transparently to the user of the `complex_operation` function."
